283
00:20:58,600 --> 00:21:02,410
Why, you...
You tricked me, didn't you?

284
00:21:02,730 --> 00:21:05,110
Playtime's over!

285
00:21:06,240 --> 00:21:08,000
Mole Evasion:

286
00:21:08,000 --> 00:21:09,120
Molefish!

287
00:21:10,700 --> 00:21:14,040
She's gone into the burrows again!

288
00:21:14,040 --> 00:21:15,500
Watch out for the holes!

289
00:21:16,160 --> 00:21:18,170
Wh-What's she planning
to do this time?

290
00:21:18,990 --> 00:21:23,790
The ground below is like
a swimming pool to me!

291
00:21:27,720 --> 00:21:29,140
A pool?

292
00:21:33,310 --> 00:21:35,270
You mean...?

293
00:21:36,120 --> 00:21:37,400
Mole...

294
00:21:36,730 --> 00:21:37,400
Usopp!

295
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:38,490
Banana!

296
00:21:43,070 --> 00:21:48,250
Mr. 4! Lassoo! You two take care
of the reindeer man!

297
00:21:49,620 --> 00:21:51,710
Show off your
400-Hit Punk Knock!

298
00:21:59,110 --> 00:22:02,840
It's no use! I can't take
an attack like this anymore!

299
00:22:03,840 --> 00:22:05,170
It's all or nothing!

300
00:22:05,170 --> 00:22:10,580
I'll have to use these three minutes
to think of a way to beat this guy!

301
00:22:11,850 --> 00:22:13,520
Rumble!

302
00:22:19,100 --> 00:22:20,900
Brain Point!

303
00:22:28,200 --> 00:22:29,290
Scope!

304
00:22:37,660 --> 00:22:38,710
Chopper...?

305
00:22:43,530 --> 00:22:44,930
Chopper...

306
00:22:46,310 --> 00:22:49,390
Now's not the time
to worry about someone else!

307
00:22:52,160 --> 00:22:53,890
Mole Banana!

308
00:22:53,890 --> 00:22:54,470
Here goes!

309
00:22:58,890 --> 00:23:01,230
You can't go after that spot on a guy!

310
00:23:01,610 --> 00:23:03,490
Quit your griping, you ba!

311
00:23:04,650 --> 00:23:11,330
Mole Banana! Mole Banana!
Banana! Banana! Banana!

312
00:23:12,400 --> 00:23:13,660
Terrific!

313
00:23:13,660 --> 00:23:15,920
There are ruins of a wall over there!

314
00:23:15,920 --> 00:23:20,050
If I maintain this speed toward it,
she'll ram into the part below the sand

315
00:23:20,690 --> 00:23:23,340
with a major crash!

316
00:23:25,630 --> 00:23:27,890
Come on, come on, come on,

317
00:23:27,890 --> 00:23:29,300
come on!

318
00:23:29,300 --> 00:23:33,050
Now bash your head open!

319
00:23:56,080 --> 00:23:57,540
Usopp!

320
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:44,450
Got crushed, did you?! You old
penguin hag! Serves you right!

321
00:24:44,450 --> 00:24:46,590
I told you, I'm a mole!

322
00:24:47,420 --> 00:24:50,050
Molehill Highway!

323
00:24:53,220 --> 00:24:55,430
What are you doing?! Let me go!

324
00:24:55,430 --> 00:24:59,720
Stop it! This is dangerous!
If you go too fast, you'll–

325
00:25:00,190 --> 00:25:05,940
In front of you! Look! A wall! A wall in
front of you! Can't you see that?! Stop it!

326
00:25:06,450 --> 00:25:07,900
Mole-Mole Impact!

327
00:25:18,780 --> 00:25:21,080
I see it! I know your weakness!

328
00:25:41,260 --> 00:25:41,850
Now!

329
00:25:46,860 --> 00:25:48,770
Usopp!

330
00:25:48,770 --> 00:25:51,740
Usopp, can you get up?! Usopp!

331
00:25:52,530 --> 00:25:55,030
Steer clear of the mole
and her holes!

332
00:25:56,370 --> 00:25:59,950
You don't have to tell me!

333
00:25:59,950 --> 00:26:00,870
Hurry!

334
00:26:01,370 --> 00:26:03,630
What are those guys up to now?

335
00:26:27,270 --> 00:26:28,480
Wh-What?

336
00:26:42,200 --> 00:26:44,450
The molehill's weakness...

337
00:26:45,210 --> 00:26:48,960
is that all of
the tunnels are connected.

338
00:26:49,580 --> 00:26:50,840
Oh...

339
00:26:52,710 --> 00:26:53,790
yeah...?

340
00:27:07,680 --> 00:27:08,900
They're alive!

341
00:27:09,350 --> 00:27:10,900
This is bad.

342
00:27:10,900 --> 00:27:14,280
The rumble ball's effect
is already halfway over.

343
00:27:18,580 --> 00:27:19,450
No...

344
00:27:20,820 --> 00:27:23,780
No more! No more!
We're gonna get killed!

345
00:27:23,780 --> 00:27:24,740
Usopp!

346
00:27:24,740 --> 00:27:28,040
You've gotta be kidding me!
There's no way we can beat them!

347
00:27:28,040 --> 00:27:30,750
Not those monsters!
They're alive after all that!

348
00:27:31,210 --> 00:27:34,220
No, we can't run away!
Not from these guys!

349
00:27:34,220 --> 00:27:35,970
Usopp!

350
00:27:36,470 --> 00:27:38,720
He's right!

351
00:27:41,800 --> 00:27:44,620
That was an insolent stunt
for you to pull!

352
00:27:44,620 --> 00:27:48,190
After going that far,
you can't just cut and run, you know!

353
00:27:48,680 --> 00:27:50,650
Usopp!

354
00:27:54,190 --> 00:27:59,660
Ha! I guess if the captain is that frail,
his crew must be wimps too!

355
00:28:04,710 --> 00:28:05,960
Captain...?

356
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:09,610
What's that about Luffy?

357
00:28:09,610 --> 00:28:15,410
If you mean Straw Hat Luffy, he got
killed a while ago at the boss's hand.

358
00:28:15,410 --> 00:28:17,840
The rebellion has begun, and all...

359
00:28:18,710 --> 00:28:21,550
You guys picked
the wrong people to mess with.

360
00:28:29,140 --> 00:28:31,480
Luffy... is dead...?

361
00:28:34,900 --> 00:28:38,570
Don't you lie to us!

362
00:28:38,570 --> 00:28:41,940
Don't you lie to us,
you haggy old mole!

363
00:28:41,940 --> 00:28:45,030
There's no way he can be dead!

364
00:28:45,030 --> 00:28:47,410
There's no way he'd lose
to some sand-gator jerk!

365
00:28:48,340 --> 00:28:53,420
You should get your facts straight before
assuming that I'm yanking your chain!

366
00:28:53,870 --> 00:28:57,380
He's the man who will be
King of the Pirates someday!

367
00:28:57,380 --> 00:29:00,260
So there's no way he'd
get his ticket punched here!

368
00:29:03,760 --> 00:29:05,970
K-King of the Pirates?

369
00:29:05,970 --> 00:29:08,320
King-er-ates? K-rates? K?

370
00:29:09,800 --> 00:29:11,950
Don't make me laugh!

371
00:29:20,820 --> 00:29:26,320
I wouldn't tell that foul story
in the Grand Line ever again!

372
00:29:26,320 --> 00:29:28,320
Man, I'm glad he's dead!

373
00:29:28,320 --> 00:29:31,040
He was an idiotic bastard
who didn't know his own place!

374
00:29:31,480 --> 00:29:32,940
A ba! He was a ba!

375
00:29:42,690 --> 00:29:45,890
Listen up, Chopper!

376
00:29:47,170 --> 00:29:49,060
A man...

377
00:29:49,880 --> 00:29:52,210
It's about time
for you to die, long nose!

378
00:29:52,210 --> 00:29:55,320
Molehill Highway!

379
00:29:55,560 --> 00:30:01,110
...n-no m-m-matter how d-deathly
h-hideous his foe may be...

380
00:30:02,590 --> 00:30:04,070
See you in hell!

381
00:30:06,580 --> 00:30:09,280
Mole-Mole Impact!

382
00:30:10,830 --> 00:30:11,540
Usopp!

383
00:30:12,790 --> 00:30:13,790
...n-no matter

384
00:30:14,310 --> 00:30:17,960
how slim a chance he has
at beating them...

385
00:30:20,410 --> 00:30:22,250
Mr. 4!

386
00:30:23,510 --> 00:30:25,970
Look sharp! Take your batting stance!

387
00:30:26,470 --> 00:30:27,970
With your four-ton bat!

388
00:30:29,980 --> 00:30:31,430
Here goes!

389
00:30:31,430 --> 00:30:34,090
Molehill...

390
00:30:42,380 --> 00:30:44,320
Junction Four!

391
00:30:48,740 --> 00:30:50,870
Usopp!

392
00:31:04,950 --> 00:31:08,680
The weak are always weak
no matter what they do! Take that!

393
00:31:11,050 --> 00:31:12,180
You bastards!

394
00:31:14,010 --> 00:31:15,770
You...

395
00:31:24,520 --> 00:31:27,800
There are times... when a man...

396
00:31:28,510 --> 00:31:32,440
must not run from a fight...
no matter what...

397
00:31:36,090 --> 00:31:37,560
You're still...?

398
00:31:38,040 --> 00:31:44,760
Like when... like when
his friend's dream... is laughed at...

399
00:31:45,040 --> 00:31:49,050
Impossible! Your head was knocked in
with a four-ton bat!

400
00:31:49,050 --> 00:31:53,220
You can't still be alive!
You can't still be able to get up!

401
00:31:53,720 --> 00:31:56,620
What trick did you use this time?!

402
00:31:58,050 --> 00:32:00,960
Luffy... isn't dead...

403
00:32:00,960 --> 00:32:05,720
He's gonna be...
King of the Pirates someday...

404
00:32:08,240 --> 00:32:10,660
I'm sure he will!

405
00:32:11,400 --> 00:32:13,160
That's the one thing...

406
00:32:13,910 --> 00:32:16,120
That's the one thing
I won't let you laugh at!

407
00:32:16,120 --> 00:32:19,630
Ha! Looks like you haven't
learned your lesson yet.

408
00:32:20,120 --> 00:32:21,880
One more time, Mr. 4!

409
00:32:26,090 --> 00:32:28,140
You think I'm gonna let that happen?!

410
00:32:28,840 --> 00:32:32,340
Let me show you a transformation
point that I've been saving!

411
00:32:46,460 --> 00:32:48,010
Horn Point!

412
00:32:48,520 --> 00:32:49,400
Usopp!

413
00:32:50,360 --> 00:32:52,550
Your tenacity, at least, is admirable,

414
00:32:52,550 --> 00:32:56,910
but despite your resolve,
you can't do anything in your shape!

415
00:32:56,910 --> 00:32:59,790
Ch-Chopper...!

416
00:33:00,790 --> 00:33:04,810
Get... b-behind... me...!

417
00:33:04,810 --> 00:33:06,220
You got it!

418
00:33:06,880 --> 00:33:09,380
Get ready, Mr. 4!

419
00:33:12,880 --> 00:33:14,350
Take this! Lethal...

420
00:33:14,350 --> 00:33:15,560
Here it comes!

421
00:33:15,560 --> 00:33:17,390
Molehill...

422
00:33:17,390 --> 00:33:20,390
Smoke Star!

423
00:33:24,570 --> 00:33:28,020
The rest... is up to you, Chopper!

424
00:33:29,440 --> 00:33:30,610
All right!

425
00:33:30,900 --> 00:33:33,650
That kid took off his boots
and got away!

426
00:33:34,150 --> 00:33:36,540
What the...?! Hey!

427
00:33:41,290 --> 00:33:43,710
Molehill Junction Four!

428
00:33:44,240 --> 00:33:46,170
Stop! Mr. 4! It's me!

429
00:34:05,990 --> 00:34:07,470
Hey!

430
00:34:08,190 --> 00:34:10,650
You guys, look over here!

431
00:34:11,170 --> 00:34:16,030
Lethal Uso-pper Hammer Comet!

432
00:34:42,420 --> 00:34:43,930
We did it...

433
00:34:44,720 --> 00:34:45,900
Usopp!

434
00:34:53,830 --> 00:34:56,830
Usopp! Hang in there!

435
00:34:57,400 --> 00:34:59,540
Don't die!

436
00:34:59,540 --> 00:35:01,170
Someone get a doctor!

437
00:35:01,820 --> 00:35:03,870
A doctor!

438
00:35:04,550 --> 00:35:05,570
That's you.

